title: The U.S. targets Iranian proxies for a second day in a row
description: The new round of U.S. strikes is far more extensive and deadly than those that have been launched since October, when the Israeli-Gaza war began and pro-Iranian groups began their attacks.

title: Why there's a basketball fan frenzy over Iowa's Caitlin Clark
description: The University of Iowa senior has been sparking long lines for her autograph, selling out arenas and skyrocketing the cost of tickets.

title: Iraq condemns U.S. airstrikes against Iran-linked groups
description: Iraqi government officials condemned the retaliatory U.S. airstrikes, saying the attacks showed U.S. forces had become a threat to their host country.

title: A year later, Flaco the owl's escape from the Central Park Zoo remains a mystery
description: Flaco has become one of New York City's most beloved characters, lounging in courtyards and on fire escapes. But it can be easy to forget that his freedom is the result of an unsolved crime.

title: For the first time, an Irish nationalist leads Northern Ireland's government
description: Sinn Fein VP Michelle O'Neill became first minister in the government that under the terms of the 1998 Good Friday peace accord shares power between Northern Ireland's two main communities.

title: Atmospheric river expected to bring life-threatening floods to Southern California
description: The National Weather Service warns the storm could drop unprecedented rain over a wide area from Saturday night through early next week, with the period of most concern from Sunday into early Monday.

title: A big idea for small farms: How to link agriculture, nutrition and public health
description: In Boulder, Colo., the county is investing in sustainable farming and helping people buy local produce. It's been called "a triple win" – for customers, farmers and the economy.

title: Here are South Carolina's 2024 Democratic presidential primary results
description: Voting concludes Saturday in South Carolina's Democratic presidential primary election. It is the first official Democratic primary of 2024. View the live results.
